sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as Charging Station (OCTT)
    participant CSMS as CSMS (System Under Test)

    Note over CS,CSMS: Test Case: TC_B_31_CSMS
    Note over CS,CSMS: Cold Boot CS - Pending/Rejected - TriggerMessage
    Note over CS,CSMS: Prerequisite: CSMS responds Pending or Rejected to BootNotification

    CS->>CSMS: 1. BootNotificationRequest
    Note right of CS: reason: PowerUp

    CSMS-->>CS: 2. BootNotificationResponse
    Note over CSMS: Validation: status Pending OR Rejected

    CSMS->>CS: 3. TriggerMessageRequest
    Note left of CSMS: requestedMessage: BootNotification

    CS-->>CSMS: 4. TriggerMessageResponse (status: Accepted)

    CS->>CSMS: 5. BootNotificationRequest
    Note right of CS: reason: Triggered

    CSMS-->>CS: 6. BootNotificationResponse
    Note over CSMS: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CS->>CSMS: 7. StatusNotificationRequest + NotifyEventRequest
    Note right of CS: connectorStatus: Available

    CSMS-->>CS: 8. Responses
